- For bowl \(B_2\) (selection probability \(1/4\), no white chips): contribution = \((1/4) \times 0 = 0\)
- For bowl \(B_3\) (selection probability \(1/8\), 2 white out of 4 chips): contribution = \((1/8) \times (2/4) = (1/8) \times (1/2) = 0.0625\)
- For bowl \(B_4\) (selection probability \(1/8\), 3 white out of 4 chips): contribution = \((1/8) \times (3/4) = 0.09375\)

